<p>View:</p>
<pre class="highlight html"><span class="nt">&lt;lift:test</span><span class="na">_cond</span><span class="err">.</span><span class="na">loggedin</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
    ... logged in markup ...
<span class="err">&lt;</span>/lift:test_cond.loggedin&gt;

<span class="nt">&lt;lift:test</span><span class="na">_cond</span><span class="err">.</span><span class="na">loggedout</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
    ... logged out markup ...
<span class="err">&lt;</span>/lift:test_cond.loggedout&gt;
</pre><pre class="highlight scala"><span class="c1">// Boot.scala
</span><span class="nc">LiftRules</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">loggedInTest</span> <span class="k">=</span> <span class="nc">Full</span><span class="o">(</span>
    <span class="o">()</span> <span class="k">=&gt;</span> <span class="o">{</span> <span class="o">...</span> <span class="n">something</span> <span class="n">returning</span> <span class="nc">Boolean</span> <span class="o">...</span> <span class="o">}</span>
<span class="o">)</span>
